<p style="text-align: center;"><i data-stringify-type="italic">Excerpted from </i><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/2344/9780306835216" class="external" target="_blank">Traveling in Bardo: The Art of Living in an Impermanent World</a> <i style="text-align: center;" data-stringify-type="italic">by Ann Tashi Slater. Copyright © 2025 by Ann Tashi Slater. Reprinted with permission of Balance Publishing, an imprint of Hachette Book Group. All rights reserved.</i></p>
			</div>
